Global Variable# kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey

tvOS 9.0–9.0DeprecatedvisionOS 1.0–1.0DeprecatedwatchOS 2.0–2.0Deprecated

```
let kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey: CFString!
```

Deprecated

Use NSMetadataQuery and NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey on NSMetadataItem instead

## [Discussion](/documentation/CoreFoundation/kCFURLUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey#Discussion)

A `CFNumber` value that provides the status of the download in progress.

Deprecated. Use [`NSMetadataQuery`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataQuery) and [`NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentDownloadedKey) on [`NSMetadataItem`](/documentation/Foundation/NSMetadataItem) instead.
